{"title":"Yeti Cycles Drops Limited Edition 40th Anniversary ASR Short Travel Trail Bike","link":"https://bikerumor.com/yeti-40th-anniversary-asr/","date":1743716107000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/MY25_YetiCycles_ASR_HERO_Profile_40Anniversary-1536x1024.png\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"MY25_YetiCycles_ASR_HERO_Profile_40Anniversary\" /></p>\n<p>Yeti Cycles is rolling into 2025 with a significant milestone — 40 years of dirt, speed, and straight-up mountain bike history. And to mark the occasion, they’ve done their best: built a jaw-dropping, limited-edition ride that pays homage to their early ‘90s race legacy. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out this killer limited anniversary edition ASR trail bike in classic turquoise, gray &amp; purple!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Yeti ASR 40th-Anniversary edition</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1990-JulieLeadersJersey-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1700\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1990-JulieLeadersJersey-scaled.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1990-JulieLeadersJersey-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1990-JulieLeadersJersey-297x197.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1990-JulieLeadersJersey-1536x1020.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1990-JulieLeadersJersey-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1990-JulieLeadersJersey-768x510.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/1990-JulieLeadersJersey-2048x1360.webp 2048w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photos/ Yeti Cycles)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The 40th Anniversary ASR is a modern machine packed with nostalgia, performance, and a solemn nod to the freaks and racers who put Yeti on the map. This bike is exceptional, and the attention to detail is perfectly Yeti. So get your credit cards ready, because once you see it, it’s gonna be hard to forget. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember, though, there are only 200 available. So you should probably warm-up that VISA quickly!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>A Tribute to a Golden Era of Mountain Biking</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-grip--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-grip--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front grip\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-grip--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-grip--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-grip--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-grip--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-grip--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-grip--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Long before Yeti’s signature Turquoise and Yellow became a staple, the early ‘90s team bikes rocked a Turquoise and Gray combo—ridden by legends like Jimmy Deaton, Juli Furtado, and Missy Giove. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-of-200--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-of-200--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front of 200\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-of-200--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-of-200--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-of-200--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-of-200--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-of-200--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-of-200--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It was a wild time, with the sport exploding into the mainstream and Yeti smack in the middle. So that’s the ethos they are building on with this callback.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This limited-run Yeti ASR (only 200 bikes!) captures that spirit, while packing in cutting-edge tech for today’s trail riders.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Modern Muscle Meets Retro Cool</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike-.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"4500\" height=\"3000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike-.png\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front full bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike-.png 4500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike--297x198.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike--1536x1024.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike--120x80.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike--768x512.png 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike--2048x1365.png 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike--800x533.png 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-full-bike--720x480.png 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong><em>So, what makes this ASR a worthy anniversary build?</em></strong> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Starting with the 115mm rear travel XC-race-ready ASR that <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/first-look-and-first-rides-the-all-new-yeti-asr-xc-race-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">debuted just last spring</a>,  this special edition gets upgraded with the all-new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-fox-34-sl-xc-downcountry-fork/\" target=\"_blank\">Fox 34 SL</a> up front, bumped to 130mm travel for a slightly slacker head angle and extra confidence when things get rowdy. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And of course, it’s color matched!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The, SRAM’s latest XX AXS Eagle Transmission drivetrain gets a one-off 3D Violet treatment, giving the bike the perfect mix of modern performance and vintage purple ano flair. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-hub--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-hub--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front hub\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-hub--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-hub--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-hub--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-hub--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-hub--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-hub--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Add in last week’s all-new lightweight 4-piston <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-sram-motive-4-piston-mtb-disc-brakes-mineral-oil/\" target=\"_blank\">Motive Ultimate brakes</a>, and a fully customized DT Swiss XMC1200 wheelset with matching purple DT hubs (a colorful rarity in themselves). Then, top off those wheels with unique Maxxis Forekaster 2.4″ tires featuring custom Turquoise hot patches, to round out the dream build.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-shock--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-shock--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front shock\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-shock--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-shock--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-shock--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-shock--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-shock--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-shock--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Chris King, one of Yeti’s longest-standing partners, brings their precision-made headset, bottom bracket, and seat collar into the mix—because buttery smooth performance never goes out of style. And because, purple ano!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And then there are even more subtle details from Yeti and friends: a polished aluminum SL rocker link, custom-engraved BikeYoke Barkeeper stem, and throwback ODI Speed Grips straight from the original molds. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s a greatest-hits album in bike form, but with all the best modern trappings!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Only 200 Yeti ASRs, Hand-Built in Golden, CO</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-logo-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-logo-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front logo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-logo-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-logo-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-logo-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-logo-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-logo-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-logo-2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Each 40th Anniversary ASR is individually numbered on Yeti’s Special Projects badge and hand-assembled in the company’s factory in Golden, Colorado. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-derail--scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-derail--scaled.webp\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front derail\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-derail--scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-derail--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-derail--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-derail--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-derail--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-derail--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>That means every bike is as dialed as possible, straight from the source. If you want one, move fast — this kind of release disappears before most people even hear about it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yeti’s always had a way of blending history with innovation, and this ASR is no exception. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s fast, it’s rare, and it’s got that undeniable Yeti DNA that’s fueled four decades of mountain bike racing. Consider this your official final warning — these won’t last long.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Yeti 40th Anniversary ASR – Geometry </h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-geo-.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1536\" height=\"920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-geo-.png\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front geo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-geo-.png 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-geo--297x178.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-geo--120x72.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-geo--768x460.png 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Specs</strong> – Yeti 40th Anniversary ASR</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-HT-scaled.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-HT-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Yeti ASR Limted 40th anniversery front HT\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-HT-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-HT-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-HT-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-HT-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-HT-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Yeti-ASR-Limted-40th-anniversery-front-HT-2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Frame:</strong> TURQ-Series carbon frame for wireless shifting, with custom 40th-Anniversary Paint</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fork:</strong> Fox 34 SL Factory GripX 130mm, custom painted and with custom silver hardware</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Rear Suspension:</strong> Fox Float SL Factory with more custom silver hardware</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Drivetrain:</strong> customized SRAM XX Eagle AXS Transmission with 3D Violet accents</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Brakes:</strong> SRAM Motive Ultimate 4-piston brakes</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheelset:</strong> Custom DT Swiss XMC1200 carbon wheels with purple 180 EXP hubs</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tires:</strong> Maxxis Forekaster 2.4″ EXO with custom Turquoise hotpatches</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Cockpit:</strong> custom-engraved BikeYoke Barkeeper raw stem</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Grips:</strong> ODI Yeti Speed Grips, from the original molds</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Headset/BB/Seat Collar:</strong> Chris King Precision Components in matching purple ano</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Dropper Post:</strong> FOX Factory Transfer NEO seatpost</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Water Bottle Mounts:</strong> 2 main frame cage mounts</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Chainring Compatibility:</strong> 28-36t (Max 38t M-XL)</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Special Edition:</strong> Individually Numbered Frames “X/200”</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Price:</strong> $13,900</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://yeticycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>YetiCycles.com</em></a></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/yeti-40th-anniversary-asr/\">Yeti Cycles Drops Limited Edition 40th Anniversary ASR Short Travel Trail Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"86523e0150f2f9b01ae69f8389305f7e745bf7d08d681dfe40153485a38c0eb8","category":"Cycling"}